{"tid":670167,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"地區小白象屢遭非議","createTime":"2018-05-19T06:39:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-19T09:04:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"50e6906132461bfa755529e2746104bff049dc01","tid":670167,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T06:39:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180519/20395325\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180519%2F20395325&d=JR2usU%2BT2p6nOzQaRXHyQ8mDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=d5eebe63\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180519%2F20395325&h=c47562d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180519/20395325</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月19日 <br />\n<br />\n地區小白象屢遭非議<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180519/large/19ls1p03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180519%2Flarge%2F19ls1p03.jpg&h=cae1dd42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■深井巨鵝地標耗資77萬元，被居民指醜陋。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】近年區議會獲政府撥款進行小型工程，卻在地區產生了不少「小白象」，當中最經典的是港島東區的「不能避雨亭」。<br />\n十八區區議會由08年起，每年獲政府撥款3億元進行地區小型工程，2013年更加碼至每區一億元，但不少工程被批評為「小白象」。<br />\n<br />\n如民建聯區議員丁江浩提出在英皇道興建避雨亭，耗資33萬元，但2014年落成後，避雨亭的巨墩佔用大部份空間，行人無法在亭下避雨，被網民嘲笑為「不能避雨亭」，最後避雨亭因阻街遷往鰂魚涌。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n由民建聯區議員余麗芬提出的南丫島榕樹灣碼頭單車泊車場2015年落成，耗資2,480萬元，共300個泊車，即每個泊位要8萬元。部份區議會興建的地標亦被批評為浪費公帑，如深井巨鵝雕塑耗資77萬元，但被居民指外形醜陋。荃灣珠寶金飾坊地標耗資20萬元，亦被指似元寶蠟燭香。<br />\n<br />\n■記者麥志榮  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180519/large/a1302a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180519%2Flarge%2Fa1302a.gif&h=038ba290&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n慶回歸藝術品　阻司機視線　惹街坊不安　 85萬元「山墳」擺兩月急拆<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n白鶴梅酒瓶口疑破裂　食安籲停飲"},{"pid":"980cc41079aaa25b85837a2b2ba04f3dce8a165c","tid":670167,"uid":120715,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T06:49:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2075000/2075939/kuifang02-_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2075000%2F2075939%2Fkuifang02-_1024.jpg&h=fb65726a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n葵芳山墳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e6386307d5562971d1d844bbb37ca2b0c4933eb","tid":670167,"uid":120715,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"980cc41079aaa25b85837a2b2ba04f3dce8a165c","tid":670167,"uid":120715,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T06:49:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2075000/2075939/kuifang02-_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2075000%2F2075939%2Fkuifang02-_1024.jpg&h=fb65726a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n葵芳山墳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T06:49:44.000Z","msg":"85萬"},{"pid":"0b35d7db4b24ee4fc8b704dae932d2ca5e51837e","tid":670167,"uid":43146,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T06:52:03.000Z","msg":"好鐘意整地標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n改善下或者翻新下個社區仲好啦"},{"pid":"0081b45a889acc2735b7b98104df5c13b5b4604b","tid":670167,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"980cc41079aaa25b85837a2b2ba04f3dce8a165c","tid":670167,"uid":120715,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T06:49:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2075000/2075939/kuifang02-_1024.jpg\" data-thumbna